---
title: Caribbean-Style Curry Beef Bowls over Mango Cauliflower Rice
description: Let’s take a culinary trip, shall we? To a balmy island where the weather is warm and the vibes are chill. This light, bright bowl of Caribbean-style curry beef will take you there. It’s served over cauliflower rice simmered with mango and cumin to bring home that sunny flavor of the tropics. No passport required. Just get into the mood by humming along to “Don’t Worry, Be Happy.”
